List of user visible changes in the release 0.8.8

-- Improvements

 * update, action 5: now supports both the options `--norpm' and `--nosrpm'

 * update, action 5: user defined values set via the `--define' command are
   now passed to rpm when building a specfile

 * update, action 6: has been obsoleted

 * the rpm4QiLinux-it-HOWTO document has been updated

