List of user visible changes in the release 0.8.2

-- Improvements

 * autospec:
   the `--eval' command can now be executed in quiet mode (`-q' option)

 * libspec.lib:
   specfile.getvars(): query `SPEC_URL' now available
   nested conditional blocks (%if ... %else ... %endif) in the specfiles are
   now supported

 * update: new modifier `--norpm' for action `5' to only create the srpm
   package

