List of user visible changes in the release 0.7.2

-- Improvements

 * update, action 2: new test to check if the macro `%find_lang' is used when
   localization files are detected

 * update, action 4 now install all the declared build requirements if
   `rpm_download_and_install' is defined in the configuration file
   (default value for `rpm_download_and_install': "sudo -y apt-get install")

-- Bug fixes

 * rpm variables with prefix `?' (like `%{?_smp_mflags}"') should now be fully
   supported in all the specfile contexts

